short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: One-click reply to comments on LinkedIn

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: We allow people to generate thoughtful LinkedIn comments by pressing a button in the comment section that uses Artificial Intelligence on top of our proprietary database of performing comments.
